{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aff26c9999","title":"周恩来在中央××会议上对××厂保密产品生产问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9df5516d9","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"aff26c9999","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8cb0aab866","type":"title","text":"周恩来在中央××会议上对××厂保密产品生产问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03c9bb5e0b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、要支持革命群众的革命行动。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21d536d386","type":"paragraph","text":"二、为了保证产品质量，担负这项保密产品生产的车间，在保密期间内，不接受学徒、实习人员参加此项生产任务。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8a41829c4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、担负这项保密产品生产的车间，有关无产阶级文化大革命的活动，要在俱乐部、食堂等场所进行。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ae1d9455a","type":"paragraph","text":"四、担负这项保密产品生产的车间内，存放绝密技术资料及图纸处，不准存放文化革命的材料，三方面应派人共同检查。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff3854f32e","type":"paragraph","text":"五、在与有关方面商妥后，可发给担负此项保密产品生产车间一个护照，共同保证此项保密产品生产任务的顺利进行。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d5853c23e","type":"paragraph","text":"（以上五条是总理指示的大意）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"aff26c9999","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}